data.description: : Nestled on .83 acres of land, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath retreat offers tranquility and space for both neighborhood enthusiasts and land aficionados alike. The main floor boasts an open floor plan with luxury vinyl plank flooring (LVP) throughout, creating a seamless flow for everyday living and entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring quartz countertops and updated appliances, all included with the home, ensuring both style and functionality. Upstairs, discover three spacious bedrooms and two full baths, along with a versatile bonus room perfect for a fourth bedroom or a cozy man cave. Outside, escape to your own oasis with an above-ground pool and a massive fully fenced backyard, providing the perfect setting for relaxation and endless outdoor enjoyment for both kids and furry household members. Welcome to your home sweet home!
